<div class="banner">
  <div class="banner__avatar">
    <div class="front">
      <%= figure_tag 'avatar.png', size: '158x180', title: 'Avatar' %>
    </div>
    <div class="back">
      <figure>
        <%= retina_img 'me.jpg', size: '158x180', title: 'Photograph' %>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="banner__text">
    <p>
      Welcome to the personal site of Kyrylo Silin. I&#8217;m a
      programmer who works at <a href="https://airbrake.io">Airbrake</a>. My
      passion is building tools that help other programmers understand and debug
      their own programs.
    </p>
    <p>
      I am an admirer of the open source culture, therefore I regularly
      contribute. I&#8217;m a core team member of <a href="http://pryrepl.org">Pry</a>,
      a popular Ruby project.
    </p>
    <p>
      My credo is this famous quote by Alan Kay: &#8220;The best way to predict
      the future is to invent it&#8221;.
    </p>
    <p>
      P.S. The <%= retina_img 'wolf-emoji.png', class: 'wolf-emoji' %>
      &nbsp;is clickable.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="project-list">
  <h1>Projects</h1>
  <%= render 'project_list' %>
</div>

<div class="article-list">
  <h1>Articles</h1>
  <%= render 'article_list' %>
</div>

<div class="trip-list">
  <h1>Trips</h1>
  <%= render 'trip_list' %>
</div>
